data.description: Take in the Hill Country Views in the super convenient and prestigious Palmera Ridge community. Loaded with Luxury, and better than new, this Perry construction has all the luxe finishes you would expect and then some. Builders 2-10 warranty still intact. The floor plan has every structural option included making this roomy floor plan a full 4 bedrooms, 3.5 baths, a designated home office, and TWO living areas. The large covered patio gives you a shady space to take in the Greenbelt/ Canyon Views with those big Texas sunsets. Please note this is a designated, true greenbelt with a canyon and no plans to develop. Loaded with smart technology, this home has its own ecosystem and the option to add and remove objects as needed including fans, lightswitches, thermostats, appliances, etc. All appliances convey! Situated on a private corner lot with easy access to major roads and close to all the new and exciting Leander growth. See the virtual tour link for additional area information. Such a great opportunity, see this one quick!
